race.comment: Open race to close out the card. GIVING DELIGHT (3) has been thereabouts in all four runs this campaign and looks ready for the step-up to the mile journey now. Should prove tough to hold out. DRIALLE (1) is two from two around this circuit and gets a bunch of well-needed weight relief with the 3kg claim. Top-three credentials. ASSENT (7) is a last-start winner who looks ready for the step-up in trip now. Shouldn't be underestimated. TOROS (11) will be better for that first-up hit-out and can feature despite the sticky draw. TAKUNAI (13) has placed four of five over this track and trip and may earn some minor money again.
